      "content": "yeah i checked the fetching logic and the database query for the coupon code seems to be returning a valid object 99% of the time. it's just this weird intermittent failure. sometimes it works, sometimes it crashes with that null pointer. any idea why it would be null only occasionally? maybe some kind of race condition or something else causing it to drop?",
